Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper focuses on the integration of video surveillance system with deep learning algorithms for video analytics. This falls under the domain of computer vision and pattern recognition. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The use of deep learning algorithms for video analytics also falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for real-time detection and prevention of problems in service consumption process. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper may also touch upon the security aspects of video surveillance system and the need for secure data transmission. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper discusses the use of video analytics for real-time customer assistance, which falls under the domain of human-computer interaction.
